name: Hamsashree
quote: Push past limits, break the mold, and show them what you're made of

name: Shreeharsha
quote: You're stronger than you think—keep pushing forward.

name: Deepika
quote: Don't be a version of what others want you to be, be a version of yourself.

name: Zaid
quote: The only thing that overcomes hard luck is hard work.

name: Kushal
quote: Play to win, not to survive.

name: Archana
quote: Believe you can and you're halfway there.

name: Krutika
quote: Fall down 7 times, rise 8. That’s how legends are made.

name: Ranjith Gowda
quote: I’m not a hero because I want your approval. I do it because I want to.

name: Brughu
quote: Dream big, work hard, stay focused, and surround yourself with good people.

name: Nandhitha
quote: Success is not final, failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts.
